title: University of Wisconsin-Milwaukee
description: The University of Wisconsin-Milwaukee brand utilizes a vibrant and diverse color palette, which includes shades of yellow (FFBD00), black (000000), green (98C646), purple (694D88), blue (5382AF), orange (D06D34), another green (5F9A38), and grey (474D52). These colors help to convey a dynamic and energetic identity, and they are sourced from the official UWM branding guidelines, available on their website.
